title: Oster 10 Function Air Fryer Oven, Toaster Oven, Countertop Oven
description: Make appetizers, snacks, meals, and more with the Oster Compact 10 Function Air Fryer Oven. Boasting ten cook functions: air fry, bake, broil, defrost, dehydrate, pizza, roast, tender roast, toast and warm, this countertop oven takes the place of multiple kitchen appliances. The low-temp TenderRoas function: delivers fall-off-the-bone tender results for meat, poultry and more. Designed with additional heating elements and a perforated interior for improved air fry performance for the crispy finish you love with 99.5% less oil than traditional deep fryers. This toaster oven air fryer features a roomy 26 Qt. (25L) capacity that can fit a whole roast or a 12-inch pizza, while still taking up minimal counter space. Fully digital display for effortless functionality and ease of use. Includes four essential accessories: baking pan, crumb tray, wire rack, and air fryer mesh rack make it easier to cook and to clean up when you're done. Cook faster, healthier, and better than ever with the Oster 10 Function Air Fryer Oven.
